{EAST's 3\H rebid shows better than average strength and six trumps.

Just what WEST was hoping for. She bids Blackwood - her plan is to bid 7\H 
if EAST has three Aces, bid 6\H if he has two Aces, 
and stop at 5\H if he has just one. If East has no Aces WEST will get a new partner.}

